edu.uga.cs.evote.entity

Interface User

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Persistable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ElectionsOfficer, Voter

    public interface User
extends Persistable
    This is the base class of all registered users of the eVote system. Each user has a name, user name (i.e., a login name), password, and an email address.
